.TH JTUTIL "1" "April 2026" "jtutil manual" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
jtutil \- JTUTIL utility collection
.SH DESCRIPTION
JTFRAME utility collection.
.PP
Use "man jtutil" for the overview. Use "man jtutil\-<command>" for
top\-level commands and "man jtutil\-<command>\-<subcommand>" for nested
commands, for example "man jtutil\-sdram", "man jtutil\-vcd", or
"man jtutil\-vcd\-frame\-diff".
.SS "Usage:"
.IP
jtutil [command]
.SS "Available Commands:"
.TP
audit
Creates a CSV file with the audio channel gains used on each core
.TP
bin2toml
Convert binary files to data statements, usable in mame2mra.toml files
.TP
bright
Calculate a LUT for RGB output when brightness is applied
.TP
completion
Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell
.TP
drop1
Drop one byte out of two from stdin and write to stdout
.TP
fold
Sorts the file by swapping two bits in the address
.TP
frac
Find n/m factors to generate a fractional clock divider
.TP
help
Help about any command
.TP
inputs
Convert files obtained with JTFRAME_INPUT_RECORD to sim_inputs.hex
.TP
log2bin
Converts debug.log, made of address=data line to a binary file
.TP
mamedb
Filter the mame.xml file to show machine names
.TP
md5
Update the MD5 sum value of all MRA files in \fI\,$JTBIN/md5.md\/\fP
.TP
mirror
Find mirrored data in a ROM file
.TP
mra
MRA inspection utilities
.TP
patch
Generate TOML patches from a hacked .rom file
.TP
sdram
Convert .rom files to sdram files for quick simulation
.TP
split16
Splits a file in two halves. Intended for 16\-bit ROM simulation
.TP
tilemap
Converts a PNG image to a tile map
.TP
trace
Compare VCD file with MAME trace output
.TP
vcd
VCD file manipulation
.TP
wav
Creates a WAV file from the given VCD dump
.SS "Flags:"
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
help for jtutil
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Verbose
.PP
Use "jtutil [command] \fB\-\-help\fR" for more information about a command.
